column2: select top # p.objID, p.ra, p.dec, p.deVRad_r, p.u, p.r, p.extinction_r, p.extinction_u,  s.z as RedShift from galaxy as p,  dbo.fgetNearByObjAllEq(#, #,#) as n,  galSpecInfo as s where p.objid=n.objid and p.specObjID=s.specObjID and p.specObjID<>#  and s.z># and clean = # order by s.z
